<HEAD>Daughter Buying Glenn Miller's Birthplace</HEAD>
<DATELINE>CLARINDA, Iowa (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The daughter of Big Band star Glenn Miller
has agreed to buy her father's Iowa birthplace and said she hopes to
turn the home into a museum.
