<HEAD>Red Cross Reopens Offices In South Lebanon</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Lebanon-Analysis</HEAD>
<DATELINE>SIDON, Lebanon (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The International Committee of the Red
Cross reopened its offices Thursday in south Lebanon after a
two-month closure following the kidnapping of a Swiss delegate.
   Red Cross deputy delegate Mohammed Bizri said two Swiss delegates
