<HEAD>One Arab Reported Killed, Eight Wounded in Clashes</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Israel-Dialogue, Bjt</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: LEADS with 4 grafs to UPDATE with Arab death. Pick up 2nd pvs,
